                            <colophon xml:id="coloph1">
                                <persName ref="PRS15490WaldaM" role="scribe"/> wrote this colophon, stating that he is both the copier and the owner
                                of the manuscript. He describes himself as being of the Church of the Annunciation (Dabra Bǝsrāt) in Žabgʷado. 
                                <!-- Possibly add LOC for church on settlement, cf. Issue #3363 --> 
                                He named also members of his family: his mother, <persName ref="PRS15489Fana"/>;
                                his father, <persName ref="PRS15491WaldaS"/>; and his sister, <persName ref="PRS15492WalattaA"/>. 
                                He gives the date of completion as: <date when="1921-11-04" when-custom="1914-02-25" calendar="ethiopian">
                                25 Tǝqǝmt 1914 A.M. (= 4 November 1921 A.D.)</date>
                                <q xml:lang="gez">ተፈጸመ፡ በወርኃ፡ ጥቅምት፡ በ፳ወ፭ መዓልት፡ በ፲ወ፬ ሌሊት፡ በዘመነ፡ ማርቆስ። ወደብሩሂ። ዠብጐዶ። እሙ፡ ፋና፡ አቡሁ፡ ወልደ፡ ሥላሴ።
                                    ዝመጽሐፍ፡ ዘወልደ<supplied reason="omitted" resp="PRS8999Strelcyn">፡</supplied> ማርያም፡ ዘጸሐፈ፡ በነዋዩ፡ ወደብሩሂ፡ ደብረ፡ 
                                    ብስራት፡ ጸሐፊሁ፡ ወልደ<supplied reason="omitted" resp="PRS8999Strelcyn">፡</supplied> ማርያም፡ እኅቱ፡ ወለተ፡ አረጋዊ፡ 
                                    እሙ፡ ፋና፡ አቡሁ፡ ወልደ፡ ሥላሴ።</q>
                            </colophon>
